h3. Expected behaviour
Be able to configure columns displayed on the search results in Internet Explorer.

h3. Actual behavior
Internet Explorer crashes when clicking the *Columns* drop-down menu in the "Issue Navigator".
!ieCrash.png|thumbnail!

h3. Steps to Reproduce
# Open the *Issue Navigator* in Internet Explorer 11;
# Change to *List View*;
# Click the *Columns* drop-down menu to configure the displayed columns;
# Observe that IE crashes (stops working);

h3. Workaround
# Perform the search on another browser;
# Configure the columns to be displayed;
# Save the filter;
# Open the filter in IE;

